	   <tr><td colspan=2>The key here is to know when the heal works.&nbsp;&nbsp;The higher level you go the less effective the heal is.  But the real issue is level of pet vs mob.  In your example the pet is getting hit each round (may be true if you blue pet is attacking a white, yellow or red mob, you should be nuking anyway).  If your blue pet, however, is attacking a blue mob or green mob he is not getting hit every round.  So the heal goes farther than the three rounds.  Granted the higher the level the more damage the mob does so the less effective this strategy is.  Through the 20's though it works great. 30's not as great, but work great in a group.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
